{
  "module": "ARR_ATOM_CXX",
  "description": "BluePrint config for ARR_ATOM_CXX. CXX is a cross-socket module with no _CPU1 dual-die variants. Has ECC-on (ECCON/ECCSBFDV) and low-operating-point (LO) test flows not present in CXPKGS9.",
  "copyTargets": [],

