      "name": "ECC_FREQ",
      "description": "ECC frequency corner for ECCON/ECCSBFDV tests within the F5-domain flow. F5=lowest, F7=highest. MUST be processed before FREQ_CORNER to avoid F5/F6/F7 being consumed by generic patterns.",
